2. WHO (2021). *Single-Use Plastics and Menstrual Hygiene*.  
3. Médecins Sans Frontières (2017). *Community Management of Wash Facilities in Greek Camps*.  
4. Amnesty International (2020). *Unsafe Sanitation for Women and Girls*.  
5. FAO (2018). *Small-Scale Soap Production and Hygiene Promotion*.  
6. UNICEF (2019). *Guidance on Menstrual Health and Hygiene*.  
